{"tid":1547923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家係咪聽到撤回就開始失焦？[同温層]","createTime":"2019-09-07T00:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T00:18:04.000Z","uid":262190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb943138a9b5b7334eb2ec6fd4d352146717177","tid":1547923,"uid":262190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:09:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔：屌你 五大訴求 缺一不可呀！！<br />\n一般市民：好似伏伏地 但至少好過無啦 <br />\n三毛：又係時候開工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無發現熱門有大量未FC 嘅post 呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家係咪以為全香港市民都知831太子極有可能死咗人呀？</span></span><br />\n雖然我無睇紅媒，但只要一日政府唔承認，無一個親中媒體係會報導呢件事㗎！！！唔好真係以為每個人都日日上連登啦，之前200萬遊行可以咁成功好大部分原因都係因為文宣呀（我仲記得個時企喺地鐵站都會有airdrop 文宣，但宜家呢？）<br />\n<br />\n大家係時候一齊落場做文宣，咪再執著啲無可能Fact checked 到嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>#We Connect Again</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"723ff24c7cf0b4adb3f362df7b8c49f7e023b391","tid":1547923,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"fafebb7e4f4e7127a4f2408d20a4520057609da0","tid":1547923,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f8a438b74de7f931f09272683a53d343d6ba94c","tid":1547923,"uid":262190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T00:11:28.000Z","msg":"s級三毛已出現<br />\n【正視聽】屌撚曬你地班連登仔 五毛支那仔混入連登撚9你地 仲有一千正皮<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dPHEwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dPHEwS</a>"},{"pid":"3b3b395427fa50b1b